<h2>About Me</h2>

<div class="card">

<p>
Biostatistics and Demography student at the International Institute for Population Sciences (IIPS), Mumbai.
My research interests include population health, ageing, multimorbidity, epidemiology, and nutrition.
I work with large-scale datasets such as LASI, NFHS, and Census data using statistical tools including
R, Python, Stata, and SQL.
